Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices Carolina Premier Properties

data.description: This charming home is located in a highly desirable and serene neighborhood near the airport, just minutes away from downtown Wilmington! This beautiful 3-bedroom residence offers not only comfort but also convenience, featuring a garage, a fenced-in backyard, a spacious deck, and a newer roof. Three generously sized bedrooms, providing ample space for your family or guests. One full bathroom and another half bathroom in the primary bedroom. Situated on an expansive .28-acre lot, this property offers plenty of room to play, garden, or simply unwind in your private outdoor oasis. The garage houses the washer and dryer while also providing the room to keep your vehicle protected from the elements. Step outside onto your inviting backyard deck, a perfect spot for hosting gatherings, enjoying a morning coffee, or relaxing in the shade on hot evenings. A recent upgrade includes a brand-new roof, providing peace of mind and protecting your investment for years to come. This property's prime location makes it a true gem. Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, you'll enjoy the tranquility of suburban living while having quick access to the airport and a short drive to Wrightsville Beach, Midtown or Downtown Wilmington. Renovated prior to 2015, this home has structural needs. We have a quote for the repairs, the current listing price reflects the deductions. The quote will be provided upon request.
